                                "stop": 10.02,
                                "byte_start": 73660,
                                "byte_stop": 113784,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in 74-942, Rizzo against Goode will be announced by Mr. Justice Rehnquist."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 10.02,
                        "stop": 121.684,
